Fourth Department,

September, 1978

(September 15, 1978) Raffalena McCann, Appellant, v William E. McCann et al., Respondents, et al., Defendant.

—Appeal dismissed, without costs, on stipulation. (Appeal from order of Erie Supreme Court—joint default judgment.) Present—Cardamone, J. P., Simons, Dillon and Hancock, Jr., JJ.
